(93, 2, '2020-09-12 14:07:20', '2020-09-12 14:07:20', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Municipality of Burgos has potentials which can serve as its competitive edge. The municipality being an agricultural sector can enhance its livestock industry which can compete in the market. Industries such as processing centers can be a great source of income and livelihood for the municipality. &nbsp;Also, the municipality is strong in its retail trade activity which is very essential in the promotion of market of goods.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tourism is also present in the municipality. The Cabongaoan White sand beach gives peaceful environment which is good for relaxation and group or individual picnics.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Comparative / Competitive Advantages', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '73-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-09-12 14:07:20', '2020-09-12 14:07:20', '', 73, 'https://localhost/git/burgos-website/?p=93', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
